=== 軟體 ===
{{main|氫OS}}
{{seealso|一加手機3}}
與一加3一樣，針對中國大陸市場的裝置，早期預載高度客制化的氫OS並且無預裝Google服務框架。而中國大陸以外發售的裝置，預載的是原生Android風格的[[氧OS|氧OS]]（OxygenOS）並附有全套[[GMS|Google服務]]，兩者仍然均基於[[Android_6|Android 6]]。與一加3一樣，不同地區版本的裝置，使用者可以選擇自行前往一加的官方網站下載安裝使用何種韌體。

後來氫OS 2.5與OxygenOS 3.5合併，氫OS全面改用與Oxygen OS相同的Android使用者界面設計，氫OS也預裝了最基本的Google服務框架以應對衆多應用程式的依賴（但仍缺少Play商店、Gmail、Google日曆等服務，仍以自製服務取代）。一加3及一加3T的系統軟體在日後除版本號以外保持同步更新，包括官方的系統軟體公開測試更新頻道。自一加3/3T起（包括一加3/3T）推出所有的裝置均會提供三年的官方軟體更新服務，包括兩年的功能及安全性更新（包括Android大版本更新）和一年的安全性維護服務。

最初廠方承諾為一加3和一加3T升級至Android 8.1。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://theappscentral.com/oneplus-3-3t-will-get-android-o-upgrade-confirms-ceo-pete-lau-news-news/|title=OnePlus 3, 3T will get Android O upgrade, confirms CEO Pete Lau : News, News - TheAppsCentral|date=31 May 2017|work=TheAppsCentral|access-date=3 November 2017|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200507134107/https://theappscentral.com/oneplus-3-3t-will-get-android-o-upgrade-confirms-ceo-pete-lau-news-news/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.xda-developers.com/oneplus-3-op3-android-o-last-update/|title=OnePlus Confirms Android O is Last Big Update for OnePlus 3/3T|date=11 August 2017|work=xda-developers|access-date=3 November 2017|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125165028/https://www.xda-developers.com/oneplus-3-op3-android-o-last-update/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年9月8日，一加3/3T的Android 8內部測試結束，推出公開測試，<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/09/06/oneplus-3-closed-beta-group-receives-8-0-oreo-update-3t-5-builds-coming-soon-public-beta-slated-end-september/|title=OnePlus 3 closed beta group receives 8.0 Oreo update with 3T and 5 builds coming soon, public beta slated for end of September|date=6 September 2017|work=Android Police|access-date=3 November 2017|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210906220028/https://www.androidpolice.com/2017/09/06/oneplus-3-closed-beta-group-receives-8-0-oreo-update-3t-5-builds-coming-soon-public-beta-slated-end-september/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年9月19日，推出適用於一加3/3T的[[Android_8.0|Android 8]] OTA系統軟體更新。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.techradar.com/news/android-oreo-update-lands-on-oneplus-3-and-oneplus-3t|title=Android Oreo update lands on OnePlus 3 and OnePlus 3T|author=|date=|website=techradar.com|access-date=2020-01-04|archive-date=2020-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200507134117/https://www.techradar.com/news/android-oreo-update-lands-on-oneplus-3-and-oneplus-3t|dead-url=no}}</ref>

不過，在2018年6月30日，一加悄然再次更新了一加3/3T的軟體更新策略，將最終推播[[Android_P|Android P]]（即後來的Android 9）的更新並停止了一加3/3T的軟體公開測試更新頻道。<ref>{{cite web |title=The OnePlus 3/3T will skip Android 8.1 and get Android P |url=https://www.xda-developers.com/oneplus-3-oneplus-3t-android-p-update/ |website=xda-developers |accessdate=31 July 2018 |date=30 July 2018 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112225920/https://www.xda-developers.com/oneplus-3-oneplus-3t-android-p-update/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>第一個適用於一加3/3T的基於Android 9的穩定版系統更新於2019年5月推出，是爲氫OS/OxygenOS 9.0.2。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.androidpolice.com/2019/05/22/android-9-pie-now-rolling-out-to-oneplus-3-and-3t/|title=Android 9 Pie now rolling out to OnePlus 3 and 3T|last=|first=|date=2019-05-22|work=Android Police|access-date=2019-06-25|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630215217/https://www.androidpolice.com/2019/05/22/android-9-pie-now-rolling-out-to-oneplus-3-and-3t/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=OnePlus 3/3T get stable Android Pie with OxygenOS 9.0.2 |url=https://www.xda-developers.com/oneplus-3-3t-stable-android-pie-oxygenos-9-0-2/ |website=xda-developers |date=22 May 2019 |access-date=2020-01-04 |archive-date=2021-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418175431/https://www.xda-developers.com/oneplus-3-3t-stable-android-pie-oxygenos-9-0-2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>而後發佈了數個安全更新和重要錯誤更新後<ref>{{cite web |title=OxygenOS 9.0.4 for the OnePlus 3/3T brings June 2019 security patches |url=https://www.xda-developers.com/oxygenos-9-oneplus-3-3t-june-security-patch-bug/ |website=xda-developers |date=1 July 2019 |access-date=2020-01-04 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411102205/https://www.xda-developers.com/oxygenos-9-oneplus-3-3t-june-security-patch-bug/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，目前最新版的軟體版本氫OS/OxygenOS 9.0.6。<ref>{{cite web |title=Software Upgrade - OnePlus.com |url=https://www.oneplus.com/ca_en/support/softwar